reviewText: I bought it to see Dana Delany and was not disappointed. It was a fascinating story of some heroic people.
Why not on DVD yet???? I would buy this as well.  I love these stories.  I would love to have a better picture quality and sound.
Wonderful story of sadness and overcoming it!
She's happy with it.  It's not the sort of thing I go for so I didn't watch.  Arrived very quickly.
